{"tid":534270,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【樂視第二】海航為出售NH Hotel近30%權益聘請顧問","createTime":"2018-01-19T15:34:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T18:17:34.000Z","uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d9f870b568e07e715b6d79ad65128b1a6fc5bb78","tid":534270,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T15:34:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1376215_1_20180119225410.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1376215_1_20180119225410.jpg&h=326bdab5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海航集團表示，為出售持有的29.5%西班牙酒店集團NH Hotel Group股權，聘請摩根大通及Benedetto，以及Gartland&amp;Co為顧問。按周四收市價計算，有關權益價值約6.3億歐元。<br />\n<br />\nNH Hotel在30個國家經營約400家酒店，集團經過債務重組後， 2015年扭虧為盈。公司預計到2019年將獲得淨收入1億歐元。"},{"pid":"f5a0008f6ebe11fac7b947c8b91acb5f9cda9626","tid":534270,"uid":68094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T15:51:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e86d8f47bd7e578bfb93b20441ff4ded48c69f9","tid":534270,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T18:17:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}